data.description: NEW YEAR NEW PRICE!!! LOWEST PRICED HOME PER SF IN THE ENTIRE COMMUNITY!!!! AND JUST REDUCED AGAIN!!!! FOR AN EVEN BETTER DEAL!!! Seller and lender will pay for rate buy down, inquire within!! Why build when you can buy now with a home that is still like new! This 4 bedroom home with great space is now available for its next owners. Nice spacious corner lot with elbow room on both sides! Large great room on 1st floor with beautiful cabinets, granite counters and all stainless steel appliances. Super large walk in pantry with lots of additional closet space throughout. All bedrooms are of good size on the 2nd floor along with laundry room and loft for added living space. Bright and airy home in a new community that's close to all.  Community pool with beautiful water views, playground and cabana. Spectrum wifi & basic cable is also included in the HOA fees. Home security system will also convey. Home qualifies for DOWN PAYMENT ASSISTANCE, FHA, VA and Conventional Financing. If buyers have larger down payment, loan could be ASSUMABLE for a great LOW RATE of 4.75%!!!! TALK ABOUT A SAVINGS MONTH AFTER MONTH FOR YEARS TO COME!!!! OR Let us put you in touch with our lender offering 100% FINANCING WITH NO PMI! Call us Today!!
